134
00:12:17,987 --> 00:12:22,241
Diplomatic Officer of the <i>Starship Ferkel.</i>

135
00:12:23,367 --> 00:12:26,454
Starship. Cool.

136
00:12:27,830 --> 00:12:30,666
I don't know how,
and they couldn't let go of their ladder.

137
