of our existence

147
00:13:00,779 --> 00:13:02,239
from your world's primiti.

148
00:13:03,616 --> 00:13:06,577
I mean, emerging civilization.

149
00:13:07,119 --> 00:13:09,038
If you do spill our beans,

150
00:13:09,205 --> 00:13:11,415
