204
00:16:24,692 --> 00:16:26,902
like strange lights, or blizzards in July.

205
00:16:26,986 --> 00:16:28,404
I've been coming here all my life,

206
00:16:28,487 --> 00:16:30,322
and I've never seen
anything strange happen,

207
